These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, cabbage, pomegranate, raspberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, hiking, writing
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, ebony, light-blue, orange
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, hedgehog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, lacrosse, sailing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, orchid, zinnia, begonia
 1. the person eating broccoli is between the person drinking fanta and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 2. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
 3. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 5. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the person who likes ebony is between the person who growsorchid and the owner of the lizard##2
 8. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the person eating raspberry is the person who likes amber##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is the person eating cabbage##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
14. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
15. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | milk        | sprite     | hot-chocolate | fanta      |
| Food          | pomegranate | cabbage    | broccoli      | raspberry  |
| Hobby         | filmmaking  | writing    | camping       | hiking     |
| Color   | light-blue        | orange       | ebony          | amber |
| Pet           | hedgehog    | chinchilla | goldfish      | lizard     |
| Sport         | badminton   | baseball   | lacrosse      | sailing    |
| Flower     | tulip        | orchid        | begonia    | zinnia    |

