The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, snowboarding, swimming
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, november, january, july
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of indie##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the fan of punk##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the fan of funk is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the person eating cherry is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
12. the person eating blueberry is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person eating cucumber##2
13. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the fan of indie##1
14. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
15. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |       4       |
